commit.message:
Revert "Fix #10: Always initialize config object"

This reverts commit c24639ff219f7ae03a5d8dc74aff15614ac43add.
Added separate test env for noopts into tox config

Fix #10: Always initialize config object

If no spark-options are defined in pytest.ini then the configuration
will be loaded with only the defaults.

Also remove a related piece of dead code, and improve error message for
when initialization has gone wrong.

Docker - Upgrade Spark version

Spark 2.4.3 is built with an older version of Scala, adjust spark-xml
dependency to match

Docker - Fix some Docker annoyances

Remove use of volume as this interferes with the COPY in Dockerfile

Provide more output in download_spark.sh script:
    sh will output which line is being executed
    wget will not suppress errors (flag -nv instead of -q)
#8: documented the configuration of Spark (including external libs)
